{"tid":1894875,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"牢牢記住除罩之約 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-02-24T08:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T08:12:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"746749f43a82b82cf0961ddec54e62cd660632fd","tid":1894875,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200224/20867966/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200224%2F20867966%2F&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=9ca3c117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200224%2F20867966%2F&h=7a210ea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200224/20867966/</a><br />\n<br />\n牢牢記住除罩之約 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200224/large/1582445468_8bf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200224%2Flarge%2F1582445468_8bf8.jpg&h=5b12ca7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">年輕人在ifc橋下跪，毋忘手足，請大家牢牢記住他們的付出</span>。<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人的2019不是世衞掩耳盜鈴的COVID，逆權運動後武肺掩至，若非勇和合璧，手足攻堅，香港已是武漢實驗室的蝙蝠，根本沒有「香港會是第二個武漢」，而是香港取代武漢，一而再，SARS重臨！</span>當然，到時鑽石「公主病號」當可幸免於疫，香港人帶住病毒去旅行，還能撻世衞譚先生個朵，高消費享用郵輪服務而不被船公司落閘放狗驅逐才奇！年輕人下跪直諫的新聞讓人想起，公主病號好像有一位與家人被迫坐艇的連登仔，未知狀況。我腦海霎時冒出船上勇武合力發揮「理大戰役」的逃生畫面，港客從船艙游繩而下，逃出這台瘟疫蔓延的海上監倉，雖然最終必遭日警扣留，但反抗與自救精神延續不休，勢必衝擊僵化保守的日本政壇，感染和民。不過呢，勇和仍然記住手足身纏N條莫須有罪名的農曆年假，怎會有心情上船「自豪」。所以有人說公主病號大部份是藍絲，除了毒舌大鬧日方不公無能之外，只能寄托無行無恥的林奠政權，後者確實使命必達，劫貧濟富，將公屋順手拿來&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n黑警飯敍播毒消息刺激下，香檳被搶了一天。黨鐵依然記得每月21號提早封關，除罩的約定下，先幹掉兩瓶Corona啤酒吧。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n==================<br />\n<br />\n多謝手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972dde9ad1572117f8f0f205310daef4ce8be08a","tid":1894875,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住左<br />\n好似約左係<br />\n行山徑<br />\n</span>"}]}